text: Enrique Arathoon (born 18 January 1992) is a Salvadoran competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Salvadoran male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of El Salvador Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:Pan American Games competitors for El Salvador Category:Sailors at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:Competitors at the 2014 Central American and Caribbean Games Category:Central American and Caribbean Games bronze medalists for El Salvador Category:Sailors at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Central American and Caribbean Games medalists in sailing
